The paper is about optimization algorithms for deep learning, specifically exploiting the interpolation property of deep learning models. This topic is closely related to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), neural networks (cs.NE), and natural language processing (cs.CL). However, since the paper focuses on optimization algorithms, cs.LG is the most likely sub-category, followed by cs.AI and cs.CV.
